Mimsy Farmer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mimsy_Farmer 0 Mimsy Farmer (born February 28, 1945) is an American actress, artist and sculptor. Her nickname came from a line in Lewis Carroll's Jabberwocky; "All mimsy were the borogoves". Mimsy_Farmer ( born February_28_,_1945 ) is an_American_actress , artist_and_sculptor .
